<plot>In the One Son, Chester is an aggressive Asian-American who starts off as a low level delivery boy for a powerful organized crime boss named Dai Lo. Chester lets nothing stand in his way as he rises to the top of Dai Lo's crime organization. Chester is involved in illegal activities including money laundering, black market merchandise, robbing computer chip manufacturers, smuggling immigrants, and exporting stolen cars. As Chester ascends to the top of the crime organization he finds out that family is not what it always seems to be. Chester learns to only trust himself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?412638</url></doc>
